PG shooter that has some neat cell-shaded graphics, a compelling story, and some odd humor and characters too. The game is set in a fictional world and is story driven action roleplaying, so don’t be expecting a quick game of Minesweeper.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo, why not grab Borderlands 2 for free while it’s available this weekend?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eHow to Download Borderlands 2 for Free on Steam\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou will need to have Steam and a Steam account to be able to download and play Borderlands 2 for free. If you don’t have Steam and a Steam account, you can create one at \u003ca href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehttps://store.steampowered.com/\u003c/a\u003e. We’re assuming you have already completed this task and have a Steam account:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLaunch Steam and login to your Steam account (free)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eEither \u003ca href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/49520/Borderlands_2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eclick here to go to the Borderlands 2 page on Steam\u003c/a\u003e or search for “Borderlands 2” within Steam and go to the Borderlands 2 page\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLook for where it says “Get Borderlands 2” and choose “Add to Account” (free until June 8)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/get-borderlands-free-steam-610x466.jpg\" alt=\"How to download Borderlands 2 for free from Steam\" width=\"610\" height=\"466\" srcset=\"https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/get-borderlands-free-steam-610x466.jpg 610w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/get-borderlands-free-steam-300x229.jpg 300w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/get-borderlands-free-steam-768x586.jpg 768w, https://cdn.osxdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/get-borderlands-free-steam-1536x1173.jpg 1536w, https://cdn